dct_description_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation. Division of Forestry, Geology, Parks, and Historic Sites. Atlas Sheet 22 (1947) New Jersey Geological Survey. Alternate title: [New Jersey.] Atlas sheet no. 22. Relief shown by 20 ft contour interval. Title is not given. Region covered: eastern Sussex, western Passaic and northern Morris. Original survey and revisions to 1909 made under direction of C.C. Vermeule, topographer in 1880-3; 1947 revision by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1947.
